<div class="comment-author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/28c42b8b0c79af8a92b654f934dc6681?s=80&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D80&amp;r=G' class='photo avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' /> <span class="fn n">Tersia</span></div>
