<div class="comment-content">
<p>Toe nie. Marellus, die jehova getuienisse glo vlgs Wikipedia<br />
Jehovah&#8217;s Witnesses believe that Jesus is God&#8217;s &#8220;only-begotten Son&#8221;, and that his life began in heaven.[86] He is described as God&#8217;s first creation and the &#8220;exact representation of God&#8221;,[87] but is believed to be a separate entity and not part of a Trinity. Jesus is said to have been used by God in the creation of all other things.[88] </p>
<p>Ek glo Yahshua was ‘n mens so ek gebore uit Josef en Miriam.  Hy is die Seun van die Mens (Dan 7:13), die Seun van Dawid en Yahweh se eerste Profeet (Deut 18:18) en  Messias van Israel wat die dood kon oorwin. Net Yahweh is Skepper en niemand het Hom gehelp nie. Dit sê Yahweh (Jes  45:7, 12,18.</p>
<p>Probeer nou ons Sewendagse Adventiste maak en as dit nie werk nie, probeer dan jode en as dit nie werk nie aanvaar dat ons net gewoon knegte van die Ware God Yahweh is sonder enige ander boeke en leringe en dogmas en kerke en priesters of predikante.</p>
